description: Gets a list of tags associated with the specified resource. Only bots, bot aliases, and bot channels can have tags associated with them.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource to get a list of tags for.

nested_items.name: tags
nested_items.description: The tags associated with a resource.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: The key for the tag. Keys are not case-sensitive and must be unique.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The value associated with a key. The value may be an empty string but it can't be null.
